As a Senior Software Engineer II, Internal Systems at Biofire, you will help build and improve Biofire’s internal systems, partnering closely with system owners and cross-functional stakeholders to understand how our systems work today and where they break down. This role is accountable for turning ambiguity into clear technical plans and shipped solutions that remove meaningful manual work and close important data and traceability gaps.

You’ll work across commercial platforms, custom applications, integrations, and data flows to build systems that are reliable, supportable, and practical for real operations. This is a hands-on engineering role with direct impact on how Biofire scales its workflows.



KEY RESPONSIBILITIES

